<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>ChillPick | Home</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/utility/faq.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="container py-5">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>

      <section class="faq-section">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="question-container">
            Q: What is the Entertainment Recommendation System?
          </div>
          <div class="answer-container">
            A: It's a platform that helps users discover movies and books based
            on their preferences, top charts, and personalized recommendations.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="question-container">Q: Is this service free to use?</div>
          <div class="answer-container">
            A: Yes, our platform is completely free for all users.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="question-container">
            Q: How does the recommendation system work?
          </div>
          <div class="answer-container">
            A: It suggests content based on your interactions such as add to
            watchlist and searching trends.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="question-container">
            Q: The website isn't loading properly. What should I do?
          </div>
          <div class="answer-container">
            A: Try clearing your browser cache or using a different browser. If
            the issue persists, contact our support team.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="question-container">
            Q: How do I report a bug or issue?
          </div>
          <div class="answer-container">
            A: Email us at
            <a href="mailto:chillpick@gmail.com">chillpick@gmail.com</a> with
            details of the problem.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %> <% /*
    <script src="../../js/load-partials.js"></script>
    */ %>
  </body>
</html>
